    "path": "/fu_useKevin3",
    "value": {
      "type" : "tutorial",
      "text" : "Contrary to the poster on the wall, there will soon be a reason to be upset If you keep going. You might end up in a conversation with ^cyan;Kevin^reset;. This is best avoided for the rest of your natural life if you have any intent of remaining sane. You were warned."
    }
  },
  {
    "op": "add",
    "path": "/fu_useStarbucks",
    "value": {
      "type" : "tutorial",
      "text" : "Yes, we have a ^orange;Starbucks^reset;. It's been here as long as anyone remembers: We cannot find the agreement we signed, nor have Starbucks been able to do so, that led to it being set up here. We have simply learned to accept it. ^cyan;Kevin^reset; without caffeine is not a thing you want to see."
    }
  },
  {
    "op": "add",
    "path": "/fu_useBathroom",
    "value": {
      "type" : "tutorial",
      "text" : "Various species expel their waste within this room. Except ^cyan;Kevin^reset;. Nobody has any clue where he goes to the bathroom, but he has never once used this facility other than as temporary storage for large carnivorous reptiles. ^cyan;Kevin^reset; maintains that this was necessary."
    }
  },
  {
    "op": "add",
